Style FvwmTaskBar !Title, BorderWidth 1, HandleWidth 1, Sticky, CirculateSkip, WindowListSkip, NeverFocus, StaysOnBottom
Style TaskBarIcons !Title, !Borders, !Handles, WindowListSkip, CirculateSkip, StaysOnBottom, NeverFocus, Sticky


