*TaskBarIcons: Action Mouse 3 A sendcommand "Menu MenuIconOps"

DestroyModuleConfig FvwmTaskBar:*
*FvwmTaskBar: Geometry $[vp.width]x30+0-0
*FvwmTaskBar: Colorset 5
*FvwmTaskBar: Rows 1
*FvwmTaskBar: Columns 60
*FvwmTaskBar: Frame 1
*FvwmTaskBar: Font "xft:Fira Sans:Medium:size=11:antialias=True:hinhstyle=slight"
# *FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Title "", Icon "$[FVWM_USERDIR]/icons/Xbluecat.png", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file=/home/doug/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc`)
*FvwmTaskBar: (2x1, Title "Fvwm", Icon "", Action `Exec jgmenu --config-file="$HOME/.config/jgmenu/jgfvwmrc"`)
*FvwmTaskBar: (45x1, Top, Swallow FvwmIconMan 'Module FvwmIconMan TaskBarIcons', Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (6x1, Swallow(NoClose,UseOld) stalonetray 'Exec exec stalonetray --config "$HOME/.stalonetrayrc"', Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk0, Title "1", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 0, Colorset 24, ActiveColorset 25, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk1, Title "2", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 1, ActiveColorset 25, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk2, Title "3", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 2, ActiveColorset 25, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (1x1, Id desk3, Title "4", Action (Mouse 1) GotoDesk 0 3, ActiveColorset 25, Frame 0)
*FvwmTaskBar: (3x1, Swallow DateTime 'Module FvwmScript $[FVWM_USERDIR]/BarClock', Frame 1)

